# Key Benefits

## 1. Improved Accessibility Compliance

### Current State

Accessibility implementation requires significant effort within JRXML templates.

### Proposed State

HTML provides semantic structure by design:

```html
<h1>Report Title</h1>

<table>
    <thead>
        <tr>
            <th>Customer</th>
        </tr>
    </thead>
</table>
```

Benefits:

- Better document structure
- Easier WCAG implementation
- Easier PDF-UA compliance
- Improved PAC validation outcomes

### Business Value

Reduced effort to achieve accessibility compliance.

